// ▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓
// ▓                                                                        ▓
// ▓   B R U T A L I S T   C O N C R E T E   ·   ICELAUNCHER               ▓
// ▓   Wide, short, anchored bottom-left. Like a site ID plate.             ▓
// ▓                                                                        ▓
// ▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓
//
//  PALETTE
//    Wet Concrete   (72,  70,  68)  ← window background
//    Dry Concrete   (105, 102, 98)  ← module base
//    Aggregate      (142, 138, 132) ← secondary text
//    Dust           (185, 182, 176) ← borders
//    Chalk          (225, 222, 215) ← primary text
//    Rust           (195,  82,  28) ← accent
//    Oxide          (140,  55,  15) ← pressed
//    Void           ( 38,  36,  34) ← deepest
//
//  LAYOUT — WIDE SQUAT, BOTTOM-LEFT
//    · 720×380 — wide and short. Horizontal slab, not a tall window.
//    · BottomLeft anchor — bolted to the lower-left corner.
//    · 2-column grid (grid_side_items: 2) — two apps per row, monument scale.
//    · Search at Top. Footer at Bottom.
//    · Zero border radius — poured concrete, not shaped.
//    · Thick 2px borders everywhere. Structural.

LauncherConfig
(
    window:
    (
        width:              720,
        height:             380,
        max_results:        12,
        padding:            14,
        section_spacing:    0,
        entry_spacing:      2,
        grid_side_items:    2,
        grid_column_spacing: 4,

        border_radius:      (0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0),
        border_width:       2.0,
        border_color:       RGB((185, 182, 176)),
        background_color:   RGB((72, 70, 68)),
        background_gradient: Some(Gradient((180.0, [
            (0.0, RGBA((72, 70, 68, 100))),
            (1.0, RGBA((55, 53, 51, 100))),
        ]))),

        shadow_color:       RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        shadow_offset_x:    0.0,
        shadow_offset_y:    0.0,
        shadow_blur:        0.0,

        anchor:             BottomLeft,
        margin_top:         0,
        margin_bottom:      0,
        margin_left:        0,
        margin_right:       0,
    ),

    scrollbar:
    (
        show:                    true,
        width:                   6,
        margin:                  2,
        scroller_width:          6,
        border_radius:           (0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0),

        rail_color:              RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        rail_border_color:       RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        rail_border_width:       0.0,

        scroller_color:          RGBA((195, 82, 28, 50)),
        scroller_hovered_color:  RGBA((195, 82, 28, 75)),
        scroller_dragging_color: RGBA((195, 82, 28, 95)),
        scroller_border_color:   RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        scroller_border_width:   0.0,
    ),

    search:
    (
        placeholder:               ">> SEARCH APPLICATIONS",
        text_size:                 14,
        input_padding:             10,
        bottom_margin:             8.0,

        background_color:          RGB((105, 102, 98)),
        background_gradient:       None,
        focused_background_color:  RGB((120, 116, 110)),
        focused_background_gradient: None,
        border_color:              RGB((185, 182, 176)),
        focused_border_color:      RGB((195, 82, 28)),
        border_width:              2.0,
        border_radius:             (0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0),

        text_color:                RGB((225, 222, 215)),
        placeholder_color:         RGB((142, 138, 132)),
        selection_color:           RGBA((195, 82, 28, 45)),

        icon:                      "",
        icon_color:                RGB((142, 138, 132)),

        font_weight:               Normal,
        font_style:                Normal,
        font_family:               "",

        position:                  Top,
        orientation:               Horizontal,
        width:                     0,
        height:                    0,
        fixed_x:                   None,
        fixed_y:                   None,
    ),

    entry:
    (
        name_size:              13,
        name_color:             RGB((225, 222, 215)),
        selected_name_color:    RGB((255, 252, 244)),
        hovered_name_color:     RGB((255, 252, 244)),
        name_font_weight:       Bold,
        name_font_style:        Normal,
        name_font_family:       "",
        name_align:             Left,
        name_max_chars:         80,

        comment_size:           10,
        comment_color:          RGB((142, 138, 132)),
        selected_comment_color: RGB((195, 82, 28)),
        hovered_comment_color:  RGB((185, 182, 176)),
        comment_font_weight:    Normal,
        comment_font_style:     Normal,
        comment_font_family:    "",
        comment_align:          Left,
        comment_max_chars:      40,
        show_comment:           true,
        name_comment_spacing:   2,

        padding:                (6, 10, 6, 10),
        label_position:         Right,
        width:                  0,
        height:                 0,

        background_color:       RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        hovered_color:          RGB((105, 102, 98)),
        pressed_color:          RGB((38, 36, 34)),
        selected_color:         RGBA((195, 82, 28, 20)),
        selected_hovered_color: RGBA((195, 82, 28, 45)),
        text_color:             RGB((225, 222, 215)),

        border_color:           RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        selected_border_color:  RGB((195, 82, 28)),
        hovered_border_color:   RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        pressed_border_color:   RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        border_width:           2.0,
        border_radius:          (0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0),

        shadow_color:               RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        shadow_offset_x:            0.0,
        shadow_offset_y:            0.0,
        shadow_blur:                0.0,
        selected_shadow_color:      RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        selected_shadow_offset_x:   0.0,
        selected_shadow_offset_y:   0.0,
        selected_shadow_blur:       0.0,
        hovered_shadow_color:       RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        hovered_shadow_offset_x:    0.0,
        hovered_shadow_offset_y:    0.0,
        hovered_shadow_blur:        0.0,

        wrap_word:                      false,
        ellipsize_instead_of_wrapping:   true,
        ellipsis:                       "...",

        show_separator:     true,
        separator_color:    RGB((88, 86, 83)),
        separator_width:    1.0,
	hot_apps_color:     RGBA((195, 82, 28, 45)),

    ),

    icon:
    (
        show:                  true,
        use_real_icons:        true,
        width:                 32,
        height:                32,
        text_size:             16,
        gap:                   8,
        padding:               (0, 0),
        opacity:               1.0,
        selected_opacity:      1.0,
        hovered_opacity:       1.0,

        background_color:      RGB((105, 102, 98)),
        hovered_color:         RGB((120, 116, 110)),
        selected_color:        RGB((195, 82, 28)),
        icon_color:            RGB((195, 82, 28)),
        selected_icon_color:   RGB((225, 222, 215)),
        hovered_icon_color:    RGB((195, 82, 28)),

        border_color:          RGB((185, 182, 176)),
        selected_border_color: RGB((195, 82, 28)),
        hovered_border_color:  RGB((185, 182, 176)),
        border_width:          2.0,
        border_radius:         (0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0),
    ),

    footer:
    (
        show:             true,
        show_hint:        false,
        hint_text:        "",
        show_count:       true,
        count_format:     "{shown} / {total}",
        single_format:    "{total} result",
        text_size:        11,
        text_color:       RGB((142, 138, 132)),
        hint_color:       RGB((142, 138, 132)),
        count_color:      RGB((195, 82, 28)),
        font_weight:      Normal,
        font_style:       Normal,
        top_margin:       6.0,
        padding:          (0, 0, 0, 0),
        background_color: RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        border_color:     RGBA((0, 0, 0, 0)),
        border_width:     0.0,
        border_radius:    (0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0),
        position:         Bottom,
        text_orientation: Horizontal,
        width:            0,
        height:           0,
    ),

    behaviour:
    (
        search_name:        true,
        search_comment:     true,
        search_exec:        false,
        search_keywords:    true,
        case_sensitive:     false,
        close_on_launch:    true,
        terminal_command:   "",
        calc_enabled:           true,
        copy_feedback_text:     "Copied!",
        copy_feedback_seconds:  2.0,
        min_query_length:       0,
        show_on_empty_query:    true,
        max_empty_results:      0,
    ),

    keybinds:
    (
        close:              ["Escape"],
        select_up:          ["ArrowUp"],
        select_down:        ["ArrowDown"],
        select_left:        ["ArrowLeft"],
        select_right:       ["ArrowRight", "Tab"],
        launch_alt_prefix:  "Alt",
        relaunch_key:       "l",
    ),

    background_images: [],
)

